sa:

  Reveal stored → development/security/password[passwords] in → Windows with → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/netsh_exe/wlan#netsh-show-wlan-pw[netsh].

  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/batch-files[Batch file] (for → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe[`cmd.exe`]) that creates a WiFi profile:
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/netsh_exe/wlan/connect-from-command-line[`new-wlan.bat`].

  → development/tools/scripts/personal/wlan-reconnect_ps1[`wlan-reconnect.ps1`] is a → Windows/PowerShell script that regularly checks the development/networking/WLAN connection and tries to reconnect if it is gone.

